# Pinned per S-1 AC-2.3.4 + R-11.
# next-auth v5 peer-dep range has not yet been bumped to accept Next.js 16; without
# legacy-peer-deps, `npm install` aborts with ERESOLVE. Tracked upstream at
# https://github.com/nextauthjs/next-auth/issues/13302 (O-7 PROBE 4).
# Remove this pin once next-auth publishes a peer-dep-compatible release; the
# launch-kit OPERATIONS.md (DELTA-owned) repeats this citation so future
# contributors understand the why and don't silently delete the flag.
legacy-peer-deps=true
